本片定于2020年12月25日上映，由[[环球影业|环球影业]]发行。<ref name=deadline>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/tom-hanks-paul-greengrass-reteam-news-of-the-world-opening-christmas-2020-1202744555/|title=Tom Hanks & Paul Greengrass Reteam ‘News Of The World’ Opening Christmas 2020|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2019-09-25|accessdate=2019-09-25|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929151738/https://deadline.com/2019/09/tom-hanks-paul-greengrass-reteam-news-of-the-world-opening-christmas-2020-1202744555//|dead-url=no}}</ref>

